# Change Log
## [v0.1](https://github.com/aleonsan/vimrc/tree/v0.1) (2017-03-30)
[Full Changelog](https://github.com/aleonsan/vimrc/compare/initial...v0.1)

**Added features:**

* Special **Python** indentation
** 79 characters of text indentation
** 4 spaces tab indentationi, even in reindentation operations
** new line indentation using regular _autoident_
* Trailig whitespaces highlighting.

**Added plugins:**

- Added [Vundle](https://github.com/gmarik/Vundle.vim) as plugin manager
- Added and activate powerline plugin [Lokaltog/powerline](https://github.com/Lokaltog/powerline)
- Added and activate folding code plugin [tmhedberg/SimpylFold](https://github.com/tmhedberg/SimpylFold)
- Added and activate pep8 plugin [nvie/vim-flake8](https://github.com/nvie/vim-flake8)

**TODOs:**

- Study some other plugins: _'scrooloose/nerdtree'_ , _'jistr/vim-nerdtree-tabs'_ , _'kien/ctrlp.vim'_ , _'tpope/vim-fugitive'_ , _'Lokaltog/powerline'_
- Python autocompletions
- Better indentation behaviour
